title: No. 5 Hokies rally for 15 unanswered runs against Villanova - VT hokiesports.com
content: No. 5 Hokies rally for 15 unanswered runs against Villanova  VT hokiesports.com
description: Packing in 15 unanswered runs on Saturday night, the No. 5 Virginia Tech baseball team cranked up the heat after its slow start against Villanova as the Hokies thundered to the 15-5, non-conference victory at English Field at Atlantic Union Bank Park.
